Package checker

Class SymbolTable

java.lang.Object
checker.SymbolTable
public class SymbolTable
extends java.lang.Object
Symbol table class is a class that stores information about all program scopes. It contains information about opened scopes (Scope) and their data, it also has a separate scope for shared data. Class also provides methods to manipulate scopes' data.
Author:
Karolis Butkus

    • depth

      public int depth​(java.lang.String id)
      Returns the (relative) scope depth at which an identifier was declared.
      Returns:
      The depth at which id was declared (0 being the current level), or -1 if id was not declared.

    • offset

      public int offset​(java.lang.String id)
      Returns the offset of an identifier within its own scope. The offset is the sum of the sizes of all types declared before the identifier.
      Returns:
      The offset at which id was declared, or -1 if it was not declared.
